{"title":"北京——平壤","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1953,"month":11,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京——平壤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这世界的东方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀仁堂灯火辉煌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀仁堂万盏灯火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀世界的东方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和金首相，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相会在一个地方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双巨手紧紧相握，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像是一座桥梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是不朽的桥梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横跨在巨流之上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它搭在鸭绿江上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也搭在我们心上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少英勇的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在桥上来来往往；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从平壤来到北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从北京奔向平壤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平壤—北京，北京—平壤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个地方，一个理想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这理想已是巨波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汹涌奔流在东方！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}